aircraft carrier replacing nimitzclass carriers now in use among the carriers features are a new reactor plant propulsion system electric plant and the electromagnetic aircraft launch system advanced aircraft arresting gear machinery control dual band radar and integrated warfare systems are also included the navy said the ship   feet long  feet in the carrier deck beam  feet high  has more than  new or modified systems president donald j trump will deliver the ceremonys principal address on saturdays commissioning ceremony a white house live stream will start at  am the nations going to be very proud of uss gerald r ford chief of naval operations adm john richardson said in a press release i am incredibly thankful for the shipyard workers and sailors who worked amazingly hard to bring this mighty ship to life this saturday will be a huge day for our navy and our nation the new technology and warfighting capabilities that ford brings will transform naval warfare making us a more lethal navy the increased combat power will enable new ways to combine information ships aircraft and undersea forces changing how we operate and fight the uss gerald r ford was built by huntington ingalls industries other fordclass vessels will be the future uss john f kennedy cvn  and the future uss enterprise cvn  the navy plans to spend  billion for the development and building of the ships related upi stories huntington ingalls awarded m for fordclass enterprise construction house appropriations defense subcommittee bill could mean more ships planes navy to commission arleigh burke destroyer uss john finn topics gerald r ford kennedy assassination donald j trump recommended huntington ingalls awarded m for fordclass enterprise construction next article nd airborne tests inflight communication system for paratroopers latest headlines white house issues executive order on defense industry sourcing  day ago ago july  upi  president donald trump signed an executive order friday ordering a r