  rio hondo land  cattle company annual sales  million diamond ford dallas sales  million scientific games corp sws group annual sales  million american residential cmnts llc his other investments include the autofinance company americredit pacific capital bancorp and  acres  km² of rangeland in new mexico in a  interview on entrepreneurship with forbes he suggested reading the great gatsby by f scott fitzgerald the financier by theodore dreiser the bonfire of the vanities by tom wolfe too big to fail by andrew ross sorkin and the big short by michael lewis philanthropyedit he has been a member of the southern methodist university board of trustees since  he is chair of the boards finance committee and a member of its executive committee trusteeship committee committee on athletics and executive committee of the campaign for smu he also currently serves as cochair of the dedman college campaign committee and on the executive board of dedman school of law he is a former member of the executive boards of dedman college of humanities and sciences cox school of business john goodwin tower center for political studies and willis m tate distinguished lecture series he has also served as a regent for the texas am university system he donated us million to build the new football stadium at smu named the gerald j ford stadium he also donated us million to the weill cornell medical college at cornell university personal lifeedit he is married and has six children his wife kelli is an interior designer they live in dallas texas and have homes in manhattan new york city and the hamptons a working ranch in new mexico and a thoroughbred farm in kentucky in  they sold their beverly hills california property to byron allen as of september  he is worth an estimated us billion referencesedit  a b c d e f g h i j k l m forbes  a b c d e f g h bloomberg businessweek  a b ten questions for gerald j ford forbes   former regents » the texas am university system tamusedu  retrieved   retri