eptember  to  he served as the chief executive officer and president of hilltop holdings inc since december   until march   and also served as an interim chief executive officer from january   until march   mr ford served as the chief executive officer at liberte investors inc until july  he served as the chairman and chief executive officer of california federal bank from october  to november  and california federal preferred capital corporation from november  to november  mr ford served as the chairman of the board and chief executive officer of first united bank group inc until its sale in  he is a banking and financial institutions entrepreneur and private investor and is involved in numerous mergers and acquisitions of private and public sector financial institutions primarily in the southwest united states for over the  years in that capacity mr ford acquired and consolidated more than  commercial banks from  to  during that period he also led investment consortiums that acquired numerous financial institutions forming in succession first gibraltar bank fsb first madison bank fsb and first nationwide bank mr ford has acquired managed and sold banking businesses and other financial services companies for over  years he has been the chairman at hilltop holdings inc since august   and director since june   mr ford has been the chairman of the board and director of first acceptance corp since its formation in august  he serves as the chairman of the board of directors at fremont general corporation mr ford has been the nonexecutive chairman of freeportmcmoran copper  gold inc since january  he has been an independent director of freeportmcmoran inc since  and served as its lead independent director from june   to december  mr ford has been a director of scientific games corporation since september   and affordable residential communities inc since june   he serves as a trustee of southern methodist university mr ford serves on the executive board of dedman school of law at smu he has served as chairman of the board of plainscapital corporation since  mr ford serves as a trustee of southwestern medical foundation childrens medical foundation and dallas citizens council he is a member of the board of overseers of weill medical college and graduate school of medical sciences of cornell university mr ford serves as a director of first nationwide holdings inc mechanics bank and auto one acceptance corporation he has been a director of sws group inc since july   mr ford served as the chairman of flexpoint ford llc he was the chairman of the board of trustees of southern methodist university mr ford served as the chairman of the board of fremont investment  loan he served as the chairman of the board of triad financial sm llc until june   and served as its cochairman mr ford served as chairman of the board of real industry inc since may   he served as the chairman of first nationwide mortgage corporation from october  to november  and previously served as chairman of pacific capital bancorp until its sale on december   mr ford served as a director at santa barbara bank  trust national association since april  he served as a director of mcmoran exploration co from  to june  mr ford served as a director of california federal bank from october  to november  and california federal preferred capital corporation from november  to november  he served as a director of americredit corp from june   to august  mr ford served as a director of golden state financial corporation he served as a director of general motors financial company inc from june   to august  mr ford served as a director of fcx he served as a director of signature group holdings inc since may   mr ford served as a director of first nationwide mortgage corporation he has banking industry experience and educational background with expertise in financial accounting and regulatory matters in  mr ford was named a distinguished alumni of smu he received a jd from smu dedman schoo